Package: snapgrid
Version: 0.3.2
Title: Common SNAP Geographic Raster Layers
Description: The snapgrid package is a data package in the SNAPverse collection of R packages.
    It provides several geographic raster layer objects.
    These maps focus on Alaska and Canada, being commonly used by the Scenarios Network for Alaska
    and Arctic Planning at the University of Alaska Fairbanks.
